### 0) Health
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### 1) Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "dummy2",
  "password": "pass1234"
}

### 2) Refresh (회전)
# @name refresh
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh": "{{login.response.body.refresh}}"
}

### 3) 보호 API 호출(예: 내 알림 목록) — access 사용
GET http://localhost:3000/notifications?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{refresh.response.body.access}}

### 4) 현재 기기 로그아웃
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{refresh.response.body.access}}

{
  "refresh": "{{refresh.response.body.refresh}}"
}

### 5) 로그아웃 이후, 동일 refresh로 다시 재발급 시도 → 401 기대
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh": "{{refresh.response.body.refresh}}"
}

### 6) 전체 기기 로그아웃 (선택)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout/all
Authorization: Bearer {{refresh.response.body.access}}
